Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,UgwDvT8O74NycvorqNF4AaABAg,,@jamesmelton7637,"""Casablanca"" is a great film. It is in the fight for best film ever made. Movies like ""The Godfather"" and ""Vertigo"" are the competition. Even if you don't think it's literally the best film made, it's surely a great movie everyone should see. 

