Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,UgwE0u-j5bWuDJLWR5F4AaABAg,,@quirtevans1977,"Ilsa was never in love with Laslo. When he professed his love for her she said ""Your secret is safe with me."" She never responded, ""I love you too."" She was in love with what he represented, not the man. She dropped Laslo as soon as she had the chance to go with the ""bad boy"" Rick. Fortunately for everyone, Rick took control of her.
