Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyzbPij1Ut0TMfJqWV4AaABAg,,@dawnrearden2374,"You definitely missed a trick not going to the Jardins Majorelle. It's stunning - I just loved the blue as it is so vibrant.  We loved the Islamic architecture but were badly scammed by the owner of our riad which has coloured our opinion of Marrakech. People constantly wanting money for photos that they happen to be in the frame of when you're taking a photograph of a building was wearing. the souks were fun - you expect a lot of interaction there and I loved that and really enjoy haggling. I don't think we'd go back to Morocoo though.  Been there, done that! I do love your videos though as they are so informative and enjoyable.",2024-11-06T15:03:32Z,2024-11-06T15:03:32Z,1,False,1.0,2026-05-14T02:01:43.989104
