Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg.AM1vhYUXWaZAM8Owh7wm8g,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Hi @96Caleb96, You can download Apple and Google Maps, but they're not always ideal for navigating the medinas in Morocco. We found some parts of the medinas incorrectly mapped, especially because of earthquakes, which changed some of the routes that Apple and Google haven't updated, unfortunately. —Judy",2025-08-22T20:09:39Z,2025-08-22T20:09:39Z,1,True,,2026-05-14T02:01:46.174990
