Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg.AM1vhYUXWaZAM8WTfayjJm,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Yes, paying close attention to landmarks helps a lot, and we tried to use the same paths as often as we could. It's challenging when you want to explore, because you can go deep and find yourself in a maze where everything starts to look the same! Some people suggest having a walking tour to help you navigate, but we seemed to figure it out okay on our own. By the time we did a walking tour, we had become pretty comfortable navigating it on our own. —Judy",2025-08-22T21:15:27Z,2025-08-22T21:15:27Z,1,True,,2026-05-14T02:01:46.175007
