Tourism,z76IT0xSeBc,Ugy9FcbQk_AcREV8mfx4AaABAg,,@kazuoyoshioka4690,"Phillipino business mindset
1)money is the first priority.
Hence their business tends to become predatory and lean towards scam.

Result is nobody wants to do business with them, they lose long term customer and profit, end up poorer.


Japanese business mindset.
Business is to do the good to the world, helping people.
They focus on creating great product and service.
Money is secondary or third priority.

Result:
Everybody wants to do business with japanese, because they know japanese will keep their promise and be honest and fair in business.
And also they provide great service and product.
So they get richer and richer, even though intent was more moral than profit.
They get more and more long term profit.

It is so true that when lord said, do not worry about money or clothes or food to eat, seek the kingdom of God first and everything will be added unto you.

Pinoy really needs to understand that, morality and integrity is crucial for the business.

If you only seek money and be predatory, soon no one wants to do business with you and you will end up poorer and miserable more.",2026-05-08T00:59:47Z,2026-05-08T00:59:47Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-14T02:02:15.509911
